br />\n我D情緒變化極大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n享受同其他人一齊但同一時間又好想任何時候都自己一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地講咩都會唸佢背後有無意思 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n極之唔想hurt人得犯罪人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想有能力改變個世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，好驚同人起沖突，同埋我唔小心激嬲人會內疚好耐，我只享受同好熟嘅朋友一齊，如果唔係就自己一個，唔會感覺孤獨，一個人睇戲行街唱k都無任何問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">最好無人注意到自己</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nexact7ly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好憎attention</blockquote><br />\n係，匯報嗰時簡直攞我命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一公開講野就語無倫次，寫咗講稿一樣狂飛啲內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇鬼片都會喊，因為我會見到鬼之所以做咗厲鬼，係因為受過太多苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59bc8ae9b82c711d1bf6798c65d3e5afeedcd42","tid":463430,"uid":83097,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T13:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又話得4%..... 咁多人都話自己係infp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣唔知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊度話得4%咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實即係100個入面有4個，已經唔少，世界人口咁多(如果無計錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得自己D性格好奇怪<br />\n好享受同其他人唔同<br />\n但同時間好討厭同其他人有分別 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddbe0c23fb03f72aff1753e1872b853e0bb7661","tid":463430,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><bloc